title: Malaysia Retail Sales MoM
description: Retail Sales in Malaysia increased 1.20 percent in September of 2022 over the previous month. Retail Sales MoM in Malaysia averaged 0.85 percent from 2014 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 30.50 percent in May of 2020 and a record low of -30.50 percent in April of 2020. This page provides - Malaysia Retail Sales MoM- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics, Malaysia
